1
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:42,060
=Twin Fire Dawn=

2
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:45,060
=Episode 30=

3
00:00:45,580 --> 00:00:46,900
Once I die,

4
00:00:47,620 --> 00:00:49,620
you'll never find Xiaoxiao.

5
00:00:52,620 --> 00:00:53,780
Everything I've become today

6
00:00:55,300 --> 00:00:57,060
is because of you.

7
00:01:06,020 --> 00:01:07,100
Lu Shaoyuan.

8
00:01:08,340 --> 00:01:10,780
I'll never give you
the chance to defeat me.

9
00:01:16,460 --> 00:01:18,060
I don't need your gift.

10
00:01:18,300 --> 00:01:21,899
I only want you to be like your brother,
obedient and not causing trouble.

11
00:01:21,900 --> 00:01:23,999
There's only one of these.
I only wanted you to have it.

12
00:01:23,999 --> 00:01:25,429
You stole something
and still won't admit it?

13
00:01:25,500 --> 00:01:26,580
I'll beat you to death.

14
00:01:26,740 --> 00:01:27,900
Do you admit you were wrong?

15
00:01:28,260 --> 00:01:29,860
(From childhood until now,)

16
00:01:30,660 --> 00:01:33,260
(I never once managed to beat you.)

17
00:01:47,060 --> 00:01:48,020
Nianchi.

18
00:01:48,340 --> 00:01:49,419
I came here specially

19
00:01:49,420 --> 00:01:51,700
to appoint you Commander of Yancheng.

20
00:01:51,780 --> 00:01:52,660
Shaoyan.

21
00:01:54,980 --> 00:01:56,059
Where's Godmother's medicine?

22
00:01:56,060 --> 00:01:56,980
This is...

23
00:01:57,420 --> 00:01:59,379
He's just some thug. Let's go, Dad.

24
00:01:59,380 --> 00:01:59,980
Alright.

25
00:02:00,780 --> 00:02:01,299
Yes.

26
00:02:01,300 --> 00:02:02,140
Shaoyan.

27
00:02:02,380 --> 00:02:03,219
Godmother's medicine.

28
00:02:03,220 --> 00:02:04,220
Don't go!

29
00:02:05,220 --> 00:02:06,739
(From the moment I took your place)

30
00:02:06,740 --> 00:02:09,220
(and became Commander,)

31
00:02:11,540 --> 00:02:13,740
(there was no turning back.)

32
00:02:20,900 --> 00:02:22,060
(Investigation into)
Gu Nianchi.

33
00:02:22,060 --> 00:02:23,980
(Yancheng Opium Addiction Groups)
Wasn't the reason

34
00:02:24,340 --> 00:02:26,840
you came to me in the first place
to make me take the fall for you?

35
00:02:46,900 --> 00:02:48,340
(In the end,)

36
00:02:51,980 --> 00:02:53,420
(perhaps)

37
00:02:55,220 --> 00:02:57,620
(this was fate all along.)

38
00:03:02,620 --> 00:03:04,140
(Lu Shaoyuan)

39
00:03:04,580 --> 00:03:06,059
(always carried light within him.)

40
00:03:06,060 --> 00:03:06,820
(And you)

41
00:03:06,940 --> 00:03:09,580
(were just a rat hiding in the dark.)

42
00:03:10,020 --> 00:03:13,820
(Your life was never
meant to see the light.)

43
00:03:37,300 --> 00:03:38,700
We were once brothers.

44
00:03:40,860 --> 00:03:42,260
How did we end up like this?

45
00:03:47,260 --> 00:03:48,420
He's dead.

46
00:03:49,180 --> 00:03:50,260
Then where's Xiaoxiao?

47
00:03:50,700 --> 00:03:51,739
Where did he hide her?

48
00:03:51,740 --> 00:03:52,859
- Did you ask him?
- Yunqiu.

49
00:03:52,860 --> 00:03:53,780
Yunqiu, listen to me.

50
00:03:53,940 --> 00:03:56,420
Xiaoxiao was already gone
when I arrived.

51
00:03:57,260 --> 00:03:58,860
He never told me where she was.

52
00:03:58,900 --> 00:03:59,979
Then what do we do?

53
00:03:59,980 --> 00:04:01,539
What about Xiaoxiao?

54
00:04:01,540 --> 00:04:02,860
Yunqiu...

55
00:04:03,620 --> 00:04:04,620
We'll find her together.

56
00:04:05,020 --> 00:04:06,180
We will find her.

57
00:04:06,500 --> 00:04:07,219
We will.

58
00:04:07,220 --> 00:04:08,060
Trust me.

59
00:04:09,180 --> 00:04:10,140
Trust me.

60
00:04:30,460 --> 00:04:33,020
I pray the Lord
reunites my daughter and me soon.

61
00:04:40,340 --> 00:04:41,100
Don't worry.

62
00:04:42,060 --> 00:04:43,900
We'll find Xiaoxiao.

63
00:05:08,820 --> 00:05:10,100
Yunqiu.

64
00:05:11,460 --> 00:05:13,740
Let's go check the shelter again today.

65
00:05:14,060 --> 00:05:15,939
I prepared some stationery
for the children.

66
00:05:15,940 --> 00:05:16,740
Alright.

67
00:05:16,980 --> 00:05:17,739
Miss.

68
00:05:17,740 --> 00:05:18,459
Please help us.

69
00:05:18,460 --> 00:05:19,860
Could you spare us something to eat?

70
00:05:19,940 --> 00:05:22,620
Mister, we haven't eaten in days.

71
00:05:23,900 --> 00:05:25,260
Where do you live?

72
00:05:25,660 --> 00:05:26,740
How about

73
00:05:29,260 --> 00:05:30,820
letting them come home with me?

74
00:05:33,100 --> 00:05:33,579
No.

75
00:05:33,580 --> 00:05:35,139
We still have a younger sister.

76
00:05:35,140 --> 00:05:36,459
We can't leave without her.

77
00:05:36,460 --> 00:05:37,099
That's right.

78
00:05:37,100 --> 00:05:38,939
My brother and I
still have a little sister.

79
00:05:38,940 --> 00:05:40,499
We'll never be separated.

80
00:05:40,500 --> 00:05:41,260
Mm.

81
00:05:46,380 --> 00:05:47,500
Then how about

82
00:05:47,980 --> 00:05:49,420
all three of you come home with us?

83
00:05:51,140 --> 00:05:53,420
But can you even afford to raise us?

84
00:05:53,580 --> 00:05:55,179
There are three of us.

85
00:05:55,180 --> 00:05:56,940
We eat three meals a day.

86
00:05:59,340 --> 00:06:00,500
That's impressive.

87
00:06:00,660 --> 00:06:01,980
Three meals a day, huh?

88
00:06:04,020 --> 00:06:05,300
Sis.

89
00:06:05,420 --> 00:06:06,939
I've got good news for you.

90
00:06:06,940 --> 00:06:08,819
We won't go hungry anymore.

91
00:06:08,820 --> 00:06:09,299
Really?

92
00:06:09,300 --> 00:06:10,499
That's wonderful.

93
00:06:10,500 --> 00:06:11,019
Look.

94
00:06:11,020 --> 00:06:11,939
Those kind people

95
00:06:11,940 --> 00:06:13,740
said we can live with them.

96
00:06:17,660 --> 00:06:19,380
Mom!

97
00:06:23,980 --> 00:06:25,700
Mom!

98
00:06:25,780 --> 00:06:31,139
♪Fates intertwined,
right and wrong no longer clear♪

99
00:06:31,140 --> 00:06:32,099
Mom!

100
00:06:32,100 --> 00:06:33,700
♪The world becomes a prison♪

101
00:06:36,060 --> 00:06:36,939
Xiaoxiao.

102
00:06:36,940 --> 00:06:37,820
Xiaoxiao.

103
00:06:38,380 --> 00:06:41,300
I'm sorry.

104
00:06:41,540 --> 00:06:42,500
Xiaoxiao.

105
00:06:45,740 --> 00:06:46,579
I'm sorry.

106
00:06:46,580 --> 00:06:47,460
Let me see.

107
00:06:48,220 --> 00:06:50,460
Mom, I finally found you.

108
00:06:51,140 --> 00:06:53,939
♪Even if time has given up on us♪

109
00:06:53,940 --> 00:06:56,380
Xiaoxiao, this is your father.

110
00:06:56,580 --> 00:06:57,860
This is your father.

111
00:06:57,940 --> 00:06:58,780
Dad.

112
00:07:01,540 --> 00:07:02,420
Hey.

113
00:07:03,700 --> 00:07:04,540
Dad.

114
00:07:06,420 --> 00:07:07,140
Hey.

115
00:07:07,340 --> 00:07:10,419
♪I still long to hold you once again♪

116
00:07:10,420 --> 00:07:13,459
♪When love runs deep,
why fear growing old together?♪

117
00:07:13,460 --> 00:07:16,859
♪Let the frost wither
the greenery beyond the window♪

118
00:07:16,860 --> 00:07:19,980
♪Even if time has given up on us♪

119
00:07:20,180 --> 00:07:22,940
♪How can love remain so calm?♪

120
00:07:23,140 --> 00:07:26,339
♪So called blame,
nothing more than an excuse♪

121
00:07:26,340 --> 00:07:29,459
♪Where in time did my heart belong?♪

122
00:07:29,460 --> 00:07:32,699
♪Even if time has given up on us♪

123
00:07:32,700 --> 00:07:36,059
♪I still long to hold you once again♪

124
00:07:36,060 --> 00:07:39,179
♪When love runs deep,
why fear growing old together?♪

125
00:07:39,180 --> 00:07:43,460
♪Let the frost wither
the greenery beyond the window♪

126
00:07:44,140 --> 00:07:45,500
Careful, sis.

127
00:07:46,580 --> 00:07:47,460
Come here.

128
00:07:53,780 --> 00:07:54,420
Darling.

129
00:07:55,620 --> 00:07:57,180
Not only did we find Xiaoxiao,

130
00:07:58,100 --> 00:07:59,820
we gained two more sons too.

131
00:08:03,140 --> 00:08:04,500
How am I this lucky?

132
00:08:07,020 --> 00:08:08,100
There's more.

133
00:08:08,540 --> 00:08:09,860
Let me tell you a secret.

134
00:08:10,660 --> 00:08:11,940
Soon,

135
00:08:12,460 --> 00:08:14,220
you're going to have a fourth child.

136
00:08:15,500 --> 00:08:16,500
Come here.

137
00:08:17,540 --> 00:08:18,540
Got you.

138
00:08:19,020 --> 00:08:20,020
No.

139
00:08:20,380 --> 00:08:21,380
Again.

140
00:08:22,300 --> 00:08:23,300
Don't run.

141
00:08:24,340 --> 00:08:25,180
Really?

142
00:08:25,700 --> 00:08:26,540
Look over here.

143
00:08:29,180 --> 00:08:30,660
Sis, he's over there.

144
00:08:41,460 --> 00:08:42,460
Then give me a kiss.

145
00:08:44,460 --> 00:08:45,940
The kids are watching.

146
00:08:49,580 --> 00:08:50,420
Turn around.

147
00:08:50,740 --> 00:08:51,540
Hurry up.

148
00:08:52,100 --> 00:08:54,420
Mom and Dad are so embarrassing.

149
00:08:57,540 --> 00:08:58,500
Stop it.

150
00:09:31,300 --> 00:09:35,990
♪How can broken love ever go on?♪

151
00:09:37,300 --> 00:09:42,620
♪How much hope must fade into despair?♪

152
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:46,700
♪In the blink of an eye,
everything falls apart♪

153
00:09:47,040 --> 00:09:50,050
♪Bound by the fate we cannot escape♪

154
00:09:50,220 --> 00:09:55,340
♪You and I caught in
this tangled love and hate♪

155
00:09:56,460 --> 00:10:01,650
♪Fragile hearts can hardly bear goodbye♪

156
00:10:02,710 --> 00:10:08,310
♪How many times
must pain cut deep before we wake?♪

157
00:10:08,850 --> 00:10:12,230
♪I once gave myself
to you so completely♪

158
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:15,429
♪Still holding on to that heart♪

159
00:10:15,430 --> 00:10:20,569
♪Only to suffer your fatal blow♪

160
00:10:20,570 --> 00:10:24,889
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

161
00:10:24,890 --> 00:10:27,469
♪Yet I approach you with such caution♪

162
00:10:27,470 --> 00:10:29,749
♪How could a stand in ever have♪

163
00:10:29,750 --> 00:10:33,299
♪The right to be loved by you?♪

164
00:10:33,300 --> 00:10:37,829
♪If love is nothing
more than endless schemes♪

165
00:10:37,830 --> 00:10:40,360
♪Used and abandoned in the end♪

166
00:10:40,500 --> 00:10:42,449
♪Still I walk into♪

167
00:10:42,450 --> 00:10:46,049
♪The trap you set without regret♪

168
00:10:46,050 --> 00:10:50,099
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

169
00:10:50,100 --> 00:10:52,679
♪Yet keep it buried deep inside♪

170
00:10:52,680 --> 00:10:54,839
♪A stand in can never cross♪

171
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:58,279
♪The shortest distance between us♪

172
00:10:58,280 --> 00:11:03,250
♪If love can
make someone lose themselves♪

173
00:11:03,410 --> 00:11:08,080
♪Then let me stay by your side♪

174
00:11:10,860 --> 00:11:12,429
♪A substitute♪

175
00:11:12,430 --> 00:11:17,430
♪Needs no reason♪

